quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,59,"Pellet, Darngal, ko ko arata, sikke alaa e mu'un. Kono ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude e yimɓe ɓen, ɓe gomɗinaa"
  40,60,"Joomi mon daali: \"Toree Lam, Mi jaabinana on. Mawtinantooɓe rewugol Lam ɓen, ko pellet, ɓe naatoyay Jahannama, ko ɓe hoyɓe"
  40,61,"Ko Allah waɗirani on jemma on, ka fowtoɗon e mun, e ñalorma on, yi'inoowo. Pellet, Allah ko Jom ɓural e yimɓe ɓen, kono ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude e yimɓe ɓen, ɓe yettataa (neema)"
  40,62,"Ko On mooɗon Allah Joomi mon, woni Taguɗo kala huunde. Reweteeɗo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno firlitortaɗon (e ɗum)"
  40,63,"Ko non ɓeya yeddaynooɓe Aayeeje Allah ɗen, ferlisortenoo"
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni waɗiranɗo on leydi ndin, ñiiɓirde, kammu ngun, kippoodi, O mbaadini on - O moƴƴini mbaadiiji mon -, O arsiki on e laaɓuɗi. Ko On mooɗon woni Allah Joomi mon; senaare woodanii Allah, Jeyɗo winndere nden"
  40,65,"Ko Kanko woni wuurɗo On. Reweteeɗo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Rewee Mo kisan; laɓɓinano Mo diina kan. Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jeyɗo winndere nden"
  40,66,"Maaku: \"Min mi haɗaama rewugol ɗin ɗi noddoton gaanin Allah, tuma nde ɓannganduyeeji ɗin ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, Jeyɗo winndere nden"